{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/organisations/building-digital-uk/about/our-governance","content_id":"a524a5e0-5a68-48a9-b34e-17374b6cf4a5","description":"The main decision-making, executive and managerial bodies for Building Digital UK.","details":{"attachments":[],"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Building Digital UK (BDUK) has a BDUK Board chaired by non-executive directors. Additional boards chaired by members of the executive team and SLT also provide assurance on BDUK’s programmes and corporate issues.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"bduk-board\">BDUK Board</h2>\n\n<p>The BDUK Board is the most senior body in BDUK. Its role is to advise the Chief Executive on the strategic direction and management of BDUK in order to give BDUK the best chance of success.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"bduk-board-members\">BDUK Board members</h3>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/lesley-cowley\">Lesley Cowley</a> (Chair)</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>Hazel Hobbs (NED)</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/steve-unger\">Stephen Unger</a> (NED)</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/ben-whitestone\">Ben Whitestone</a> (Interim CEO)</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/matt-agar\">Matt Agar</a> (Strategy Director)</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>Kevin Adams (DSIT Representative)</p>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"example\">\n  <p>Read the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/register-of-interests-for-building-digital-uk-board\">BDUK Board register of interests</a>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>","change_history":[{"note":"BDUK Board members updated and ARAC section removed.","public_timestamp":"2026-02-17T10:48:02Z"},{"note":"Some BDUK Board and ARAC members have been amended. ","public_timestamp":"2025-10-07T12:47:00Z"},{"note":"Lesley Cowley has been included as Chair of BDUK from 1st July. ","public_timestamp":"2025-07-01T08:00:00Z"},